@startuml
title Calculator Class Structure

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Calculator {
    + add(a: numeric, b: numeric) : numeric
    + subtract(a: numeric, b: numeric) : numeric
    + multiply(a: numeric, b: numeric) : numeric
    + divide(a: numeric, b: numeric) : numeric
}

note right of Calculator
  divide() delegates to Python's / operator
  ZeroDivisionError raised natively on b=0
end note

@enduml
